{"tid":900623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fake news 累死人！墨西哥兩男子被當拐子佬遭活活燒死！","createTime":"2018-11-13T11:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T12:08:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"387a3d23c572888246e61ea773b407f0051cda46","tid":900623,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:31:15.000Z","msg":"網路謠言真的害死人！墨西哥小鎮阿卡特蘭（Acatlan）一對叔侄，被誣陷為誘拐兒童販賣器官的黑心惡棍，消息隨著通訊軟體傳遍全鎮，憤怒的鎮民闖入警察局，把無辜的叔侄倆痛毆一頓縱火燒死，受害人的母親從網路直播目睹兒子遇害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但卻無力阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181113/640_2b5226867750887f919107250bc41f9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181113%2F640_2b5226867750887f919107250bc41f9d.jpg&h=dfefe550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暴民闖入警局，毆打燒死佛羅雷斯叔侄（右）。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n21歲的佛羅雷斯（Ricardo Flores）出生於阿卡特蘭鎮，但後來不住在鎮上，叔叔亞伯特也不是鎮民，他倆日前到阿卡特蘭鎮買工程用品，卻因滋擾治安被關在警局，結果不知誰在Whatsapp上面放消息指稱，這兩人是黑心人口販子，販賣幼童的器官，傳言說：「過去幾天，有4歲、8歲、14歲的孩子突然失蹤，找到屍體時，發現他們已被開堂剖腹，器官已被挖走，相信我，綁架犯就在這裡。」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181113/1465812/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181113%2F1465812%2F&d=PYL5ImRlc6bw7cq%2Be%2Brci6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1531e4aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181113%2F1465812%2F&h=03ad7d0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181113/1465812/</a>"},{"pid":"c358e3e62cfcb781e9f9140ccc07d9280b212b53","tid":900623,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"asshole國"},{"pid":"c7c36ff1970ab3fdfd2f72613250e02a2e41baf9","tid":900623,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"暴徒當中，馬丁尼茲大量在網路散播傳言，另一人則敲響小鎮警鐘，跟鎮民說，警察要把壞人放走了，還有一人則用「大聲公」要求民眾捐款買汽油，他們想要燒死壞蛋。<br />\n<br />\n儘管警察再三說明，佛羅雷斯叔侄不是綁架犯，他們只是因為小事被關，但150名暴民群情激憤，根本不聽警察解釋，他們硬闖警局，打開佛羅雷斯的牢房，拖出兩人痛毆並澆汽油燒死。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181113/640_8753f857f9ae18927057ff2647e13120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181113%2F640_8753f857f9ae18927057ff2647e13120.jpg&h=abc40d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暴民私刑過程都被上傳網路直播。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n佛羅雷斯的母親在臉書看到直播，一再留言表示「別殺我兒子，他不是綁架犯」，但無人理會，暴民殘殺過程還拿出手機來，邊拍邊喝采。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生後，警方起訴帶動煽動的9人，另有4人在逃，地方首長艾隆索表示，因為警力有限，無力保護佛羅雷斯叔侄，她強烈譴責私刑暴力。"},{"pid":"7ec00b1fa3cddec2fa7118eca48450665902eae1","tid":900623,"uid":216553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"同巴西一樣都係痴撚線國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb1e7958618d01439b91b7b574dd849962de5d4","tid":900623,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"又係左膠累事。"},{"pid":"a88fef08c3af0b2d5a4589ca49205746376f64f1","tid":900623,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:37:25.000Z","msg":"之前有港女話墨西哥好正好住..."},{"pid":"4abd66efdbf19c3c58f615f2b1f837ecc32197d3","tid":900623,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"入侵美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6becbbd743c04370291428b3873084a345f0f7c","tid":900623,"uid":48796,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"黑幫毒梟唔理，走去殺錯良民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a6bc077c459668422cc3d4743ad00a37efa